osoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>一、生产工序扫描自动化</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">利用数据采集平台，结合传感器、PLC控制器以及工业电脑，代替产线人员进行工序点的采集，解决生产线节点人工扫描效率低、人工成本高的问题。</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">方案核心构成：自动化扫描平台软件+工业数据扫描平台+PLC控制器。</span></li></ul><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.china-code.com/upload/201608/01/201608011421428170.png\" width=\"761\" height=\"201\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 669px; height: 198px;\"></p><div align=\"left\" style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\"><br></p><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\"></span><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>二、生产上料智能化</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(116, 116, 116); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">利用物联网技术实现物料预警、自动配送的效果。</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px